	MSG("It seems the lord of the Lyndale Lakes region|was stricken ill and has been bedridden for|many years.")
	MSG("They say it's an unusual|sort of sickness, though...")
	MSG("I've heard that it's thanks to his wise|rule that this land has stayed so peaceful,|so I hope he recovers soon.")
	room_flag_on(2)
