	on_jump TALK4_3

	MSG("Now, this is just somethin'|my old man told me, but...")
	MSG("Long, long ago, there was a great blazin'|spirit who lived on Eaglet Mountain.")
	MSG("That spirit used its flamin' sword to|control the fire and lava of the land.")
	MSG("The island of Harlech was originally created|by the eruption of Eaglet Mountain.")
	MSG("I wouldn't say that li'l bit of fire and|smoke was the work of that spirit, though.")
	room_flag_on(5)
