TALK3_1:
	MSG("Hey, you there. Ain't you the knight goin'|'round the ruins that people are talkin'|about?")
	MSG("If'n you go to Eaglet Mountain, any|chance you could check on the lift?")
	MSG("Just a li'l while ago, you could use|that lift to get up the mountain.")
	MSG("But with the machine broken,|there's no way to get it back down.")
	MSG("Dammit all... With it outta commission|like that I can't get back to work.")
	room_flag_on(5)
