TALK4_1:
	MSG("You wanna hear about the phoenix?|'Tis a legend 'round these parts.")
	MSG("They say the phoenix came from an age long past|to watch over and protect this country.")
	MSG("If left alone, it's believed people would|lead the world in a bad direction, you see.")
	MSG("Though, lookin' back on the history|of our world, it's hard to say if|that's been a bad thing or a good one.")
	MSG("If'n bad things happen, then they get returned|towards good. The phoenix is at the core of|maintainin' that balance between good and evil.")
	MSG("When the world has reached the pinnacle of chaos,|legend has it a hero will be guided hither.")
	room_flag_on(6)
	jump EXIT

