	MSG("Today is rather warm...")
	MSG("Maybe I should go for a dip, hmm.")
	MSG("You look rather hot too, what with|all that armor on. Care to join me?")
	MSG("We can move on together and forget|our unpleasant memories!")
	jump EXIT

//▼ガーディアン取得後
TALK2:
	MSG("Yesterday, I heard about a traveler|who was gravely injured...")
	MSG("Oh my, could that have been you?")
	MSG("No...that's quite impossible.|You wouldn't look as well as|you do if it were so.")
	jump EXIT

//▼ゲーム開始直後
TALK1:
	check_room_flag(10)
	on_jump TALK1_2

TALK1_1:
	MSG("Ah, a newcomer to our fair town.|Welcome! Welcome to Harlech!")
	MSG("You just came in on that boat, right?|This island is amazing. The breeze coming off|the lake feels great on the skin, doesn't it?")
	MSG("This isn't a very big town, but I think you'll|find it has all the comforts of home.")
	MSG("I hope very much that you enjoy your stay here.")
	room_flag_on(10)
	jump EXIT

//　　★繰り返し
TALK1_2:
	MSG("This isn't a very big town, but I think you'll|find it has all the comforts of home.")
	MSG("I hope very much that you enjoy your stay here.")
	jump EXIT

EXIT:
